Our findings illustrated in Figs. 2 and 6, clearly demonstrate a significant reduction in friction forces and damage levels in the presence of a two-subunit MUC1, attributable to the cleavable SEA domain (see Table 5). With regards to energy dissipation \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
